<p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_b7053b17-cd35-48c0-8abe-9346d1365fc0" id="_b7053b17-cd35-48c0-8abe-9346d1365fc0"></a>encryption algorithm that encrypts a plaintext into an equivalent
sized ciphertext, using an identical key for encryption and
decryption</p>
</div>
